          "question": "<p><a name=\"21004\"></a><div itemprop=\"text\"><p>It is required to divide the \\( 2n \\) members of a club into \\( n \\) disjoint teams of \\( 2 \\) members each. The teams are not labelled. The number of ways in which this can be done is:</p>\n\n</div><br><br><b>Combinatory: TIFR CSE 2012 | Part A | Question: 7</b></p>",
